<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu'n ei hehpih ka he'i,
 Bible-in ei hilh ziekin;
 Naupang Amah a ahiu,
 A hat puou, A mah a hat.

[V2]
 Isu'n ei hehpih (3)
 Bible-in ei hilh hi!

[V3]
 2. Isun ei umpih, A thii,
 Van kawtkhak chuh hawng dingin;
 Ka gitloh sawp thieng in a,
 A naupang te'n zuon u hen.

[V4]
 3. Isun ei umpih ina,
 Lamtawn ah ei pui intin;
 Ka hehpih chun ka thih tieng,
 Van In ah ei pui ina.</lyrics>
<title>JESUS LOVES ME!</title>
<hymn_number>414</hymn_number>
</song>